<plot>A rookie FBI agent, Jo Dee Foster ('Billy Zane'(qv)), has been assigned to work on the case of the Psycho Killer, a killer who has killed over 120 people. But to find out more about the Psycho Killer, Jo is forced to meet Dr. Animal Cannibal Pizza ('Dom DeLuise'(qv)), a famous doctor turned cannibal who ate pizzas with human body parts. Meanwhile, Jo's girlfriend, Jane Wine ('Charlene Tilton'(qv)), has just stolen $400,000 in cash from her money-hungry boss, Mr. Laurel ('Rip Taylor'(qv)), so she and Jo can be happy, but gets lost in a really horrible storm, caused mostly by a special effects crew behind her car, and stops at the Cemetery Motel, where the owner, Antonio Motel ('Ezio Greggio'(qv)), is dominated by his insane mother ('Shelly Winters'(qv)).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?259398</url></doc>
